bilingual.source: Being a celebrity is not always easy.
bilingual.target: 成为名人并不总是那么容易。
她是一个非常有影响力的名人。
这位名人的护卫非常警惕。

bilingual.source: The celebrity has followers all over the world.
bilingual.target: 这个名人的从者遍布全球。

bilingual.source: The movie made him a celebrity overnight.
bilingual.target: 这部电影让他一夜之间成为名人。

bilingual.source: The media loves to report on celebrity scandals.
bilingual.target: 媒体喜欢报道名人的丑闻。

bilingual.source: The bodyguards escort the celebrity to the event.
bilingual.target: 保镖护送名人到活动现场。

bilingual.source: They invited a celebrity to host the event.
bilingual.target: 他们邀请了一个名人来主持活动。

bilingual.source: He felt like a celebrity riding in the limo.
bilingual.target: 他坐在豪华轿车里感觉像个名人。

bilingual.source: The celebrity was mobbed by fans at the airport.
bilingual.target: 那位名人在机场被粉丝围攻了。

list.abstract: Nguyễn Phước Long Hiệp，游戏ID：Celebrity，越南《英雄联盟》男子电竞职业选手，现为Team Secret战队AD。

yingyinNormal.en: So what other celebrity genitalia have you handled?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还经手过哪些名人的生殖器？

yingyinNormal.en: There should be no value to his pseudo-celebrity here! And even at Star Trek conventions, they only let him in if he helps set up!
yingyinNormal.zh: 像这种伪名人根本不值得为他开后门！即使是在《星际迷航》里，如果他是来帮忙的才放他进去呢！

yingyinNormal.en: Global news coverage, celebrity visitors. Eyes of the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 全球新闻头条，各界名流参观，世界瞩目。

yingyinNormal.en: When I got home, I was a national celebrity, famouser even than Captain Kangaroo.
yingyinNormal.zh: 回家以后，我成了全国有名的人物，比袋鼠船长还要有名。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah. They say don't meet your heroes. Don't peek behind that curtain of fame and celebrity.
yingyinNormal.zh: 常言道"英雄真面目见不得"，不要去偷窥他们名誉背后的真实身份。

yingyinNormal.en: Sadly, all this comes too late for the detective, who became something of a celebrity two years ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可惜一切都迟了，这位大侦探，两年前刚扬名立万。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, because I had been a football star and war hero and national celebrity and a shrimping boat captain and a college graduate, the city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama, decided to get together and offered me a fine job.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在因为我成了足球明星和战争英雄，以及全国知名的人物和捕虾船的船长，以及大学毕业生，亚拉巴马州绿茵镇的父老乡亲，决定给我一个好工作。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: They're part of a bunch of <highlight>celebrities</highlight> starring in a new video for World Environment Day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们是出演世界环境日新视频的那群名人中的一员。

examination_example.sentence: Some <highlight>celebrities</highlight> star in a new video to urge consumers to cut the use of plastics.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些名人出演了一个新视频，呼吁消费者减少使用塑料。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

sense_info_list.en: a famous person, especially in the entertainment business

examination_example.sentence: It is based on the real-life experiences of some <highlight>celebrities</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它以一些名人的真实生活经历为基础。

examination_example.sentence: Now there's a lot more evidence of how powerful a <highlight>celebrity</highlight>—especially a professional athlete—can be in influencing children's behavior.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 现在有更多的证据表明名人，尤其是职业运动员，在影响儿童行为方面有多么强大。

examination_example.sentence: Cooking is an occasional hobby and a vehicle for <highlight>celebrity</highlight> chefs.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 烹饪成为了一种偶尔的爱好和名厨（展露厨艺）的手段。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

examination_example.sentence: When you become a <highlight>celebrity</highlight>, you have been a good role model too.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你成为一个名人时，你也一直是一个好的榜样。

examination_example.sentence: I think everyone should try to be a good role model, even if you are not a <highlight>celebrity</highlight>!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我认为每个人都应该努力成为一个好的榜样，即使你不是一个名人！

examination_example.sentence: It’s a <highlight>celebrity</highlight>'s job to be a good role model because people usually look up to stars.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 做一个好的榜样是名人的工作，因为人们通常会仰视明星。
